102
00:05:15,890 --> 00:05:16,500
Go on.

103
00:05:20,850 --> 00:05:21,570
What are you doing here?

104
00:05:22,450 --> 00:05:23,100
Where are the others?

105
00:05:24,290 --> 00:05:25,380
