220
00:11:42,610 --> 00:11:43,300
here for?

221
00:11:44,250 --> 00:11:45,180
This case has been transferred to

222
00:11:45,180 --> 00:11:45,820
my Ministry of Justice long ago.

223
00:11:46,660 --> 00:11:47,660
