248
00:12:47,610 --> 00:12:49,020
When you came to offer condolences,

249
00:12:49,420 --> 00:12:50,210
a kid around seven years old

250
00:12:50,300 --> 00:12:51,420
was with you back then.

251
00:12:51,850 --> 00:12:54,610
