leaning on his cane.

911
00:40:22,250 --> 00:40:23,770
Everyone was worried sick.

912
00:40:23,890 --> 00:40:26,050
They all went out to look for you.

913
00:40:26,610 --> 00:40:28,170
Only I was left at home.

914
00:40:28,170 --> 00:40:29,210
