915
00:40:31,210 --> 00:40:32,290
They all went out for me?

916
00:40:32,690 --> 00:40:33,610
What else could it be?

917
00:40:34,090 --> 00:40:35,130
You are one of our family.

918
00:40:35,290 --> 00:40:36,730
We love family.

919
00:40:37,450 --> 00:40:39,450
